        "content": "<hr class=\"ghq-card-content__horizontal-rule\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"DIVIDER\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">When there is a CREDIT <span class=\"ghq-card-content__text-color\" style=\"color:#00bcd6\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"TEXT_COLOR\">(in blue)</span> on an invoice account, it is due to a return being applied to the invoice. This dollar amount is not refundable and must be used towards an invoice payment. </p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\"><span class=\"ghq-card-content__image-container\"><img class=\"ghq-card-content__image\" style=\"width:650px\" src=\"https://api.getguru.com/files/view/70880aeb-f6ed-4308-bc05-6c8808ae6b9f\" width=\"650\" alt=\"2019-03-16_09h08_50.png\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"IMAGE\" data-ghq-card-content-image-filename=\"2019-03-16_09h08_50.png\"></span></p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\"></p><hr class=\"ghq-card-content__horizontal-rule\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"DIVIDER\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\"><span class=\"ghq-card-content__image-container\"><img class=\"ghq-card-content__image\" style=\"width:650px\" src=\"https://api.getguru.com/files/view/ff391d85-9289-4ad9-8401-9f10d5ed4197\" width=\"650\" alt=\"2019-03-16_09h56_31.png\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"IMAGE\" data-ghq-card-content-image-filename=\"2019-03-16_09h56_31.png\"></span></p>",
