        "content": "<hr class=\"ghq-card-content__horizontal-rule\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"DIVIDER\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Fingerprint readers are a secure method of logging into PostalMate, CashMate, Security and the Time Clock.</p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Supported Model: &nbsp;Digital Persona 400 fingerprint reader.</p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Visit <a href=\"http://olsonives.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"ghq-card-content__link\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"LINK\">www.olsonives.com</a> for ordering information.</p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Install the driver (do this before plugging in the fingerprint reader to your computer)&nbsp;</p><ol start=\"1\" class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST\"><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Choose the link for Driver download</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Run the Setup.msi</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Follow the on-screen instructions to complete the installation</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Re-start your computer after the install is complete</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Once the computer has re-started, plug in the fingerprint reader</p></li></ol><h2 class=\"ghq-card-content__medium-heading\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"MEDIUM_HEADING\">Enroll User Fingerprints</h2><ol start=\"1\" class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST\"><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">In System Utilities, choose Security Settings from the main screen</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Choose Add/Edit Users</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Add a new user, or Edit an existing user</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Choose Enroll/verify fingerprint(s) (This option will only be available when the fingerprint reader is installed)</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Choose Enroll</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Click on the image for which you wish to enroll a fingerprint</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Place your finger (the same finger that you selected on the screen) on the fingerprint reader. You'll get a message if the scan was successful</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Repeat the same finger four times</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Enroll up to three fingers</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Click OK when done</p></li></ol><h2 class=\"ghq-card-content__medium-heading\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"MEDIUM_HEADING\">Log-on Settings</h2><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Choose how users will log-in</p><ol start=\"1\" class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST\"><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Remain in Security Settings</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Choose the Log-on Settings tab</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Choose which applications will require a fingerprint log-on<br>(PostalMate, CashMate, Time Clock and Secure areas)</p></li></ol><h2 class=\"ghq-card-content__medium-heading\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"MEDIUM_HEADING\">Using the fingerprint reader</h2><ol start=\"1\" class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST\"><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Anytime a log-on is required, you'll see a screen prompting you to place your finger on the fingerprint reader</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Place your finger on the reader and you'll be logged in</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Optionally, you always have the option to log-in by user name. Click Log on by name on the Log on screen</p></li></ol><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">How to get to the fingerprint driver install</p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">In System Utilities, choose <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Tools </strong>&gt; <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Security </strong>&gt; <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Fingerprint device</strong>...</p><hr class=\"ghq-card-content__horizontal-rule\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"DIVIDER\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\"> If you find that you are unable to register your digits:  </p><ul start=\"1\" class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST\"><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">make sure the factory film sheet is removed from the fingerprint reader</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">try using your less dominant hand to scan and register </p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">try wiping off the reader from smudges and dirt</p></li></ul>",
