        "content": "<p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">This error occurs when the fingerprint device is the desired login, but no users have fingerprints added.  This error will appear.  The resolution is to set the PM Utilities &gt; Security Settings &gt; [TAB] Log-on Settings to name, instead of Fingerprint reader.  </p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\"><span class=\"ghq-card-content__image-container\"><img class=\"ghq-card-content__image\" style=\"width:594px\" src=\"https://api.getguru.com/files/view/5e117e83-9bc6-427d-a2e4-995b97f606f1\" width=\"594\" alt=\"image.png\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"IMAGE\" data-ghq-card-content-image-filename=\"image.png\"></span></p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Next go into Edit User and Enroll Fingerprints.  Then, switch the log-on back to Fingerprint reader.  This will resolve the error.</p><hr class=\"ghq-card-content__horizontal-rule\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"DIVIDER\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">If you find that you are unable to register your digits:  </p><ul start=\"1\" class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST\"><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">make sure the factory film sheet is removed from the fingerprint reader</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">try using your less dominant hand to scan and register </p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">try wiping off the reader from smudges and dirt</p></li></ul>",
