    {
        "content": "<p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\"> All Benavides store are based on Enterprise level set up. </p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Except  Receipt header, FedEx HAL Agent  ID, FedEx HAL Location ID.</p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">There are three packages:</p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\"> 1) Envelope  32*2*39</p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">2) Large = 27*27*27</p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\"> 3) Medium = 20*20*20</p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\"><strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Benavides sets to use Google place &gt; </strong> google is 2 in web portal</p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\"> IF there is no FedEx office close the <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">store </strong>location it does not show the FedEx office address in message box.</p>",
