    {
        "content": "<p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\"><strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Updated: Setting the Test Defaults using CTRL + ALT +SHIFT +S in PM Utilities will automatically set this. </strong></p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\"><strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Update: Set it to Production Servers while in Test Environment and use the New Fedex Production Account in both FedEx Service and FedEx F Box to see rates  (12/20/18)</strong></p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">There are certain configurations that need to be undertaken so as to use the FedEx Freight box feature:</p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\"><span class=\"ghq-card-content__image-container\"><img class=\"ghq-card-content__image\" style=\"width:650px\" src=\"https://api.getguru.com/files/view/dd51009b-e014-41d7-bd98-23829783e794\" width=\"650\" alt=\"image.png\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"IMAGE\" data-ghq-card-content-image-filename=\"image.png\"></span></p><h2 class=\"ghq-card-content__medium-heading\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"MEDIUM_HEADING\">Go to PM Utilities </h2><ol start=\"1\" class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST\"><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Activate hidden menu by using Ctrl +Alt+Shift+S</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Tools &gt; Set Servers (enter password \"mmddyy999999\") &gt; FedEx Webservice server = 9 and FedEx F Box Webservice = 43 &gt; Update</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Exit PMU and Open PM</p></li></ol><h2 class=\"ghq-card-content__medium-heading\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"MEDIUM_HEADING\">Within PostalMate Settings in PM, perform the following actions....</h2><ol start=\"1\" class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST\"><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Carrier Setup: Navigate to FedEx tab &gt; Online shipping: Subscribe online with FedEx</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Enter FedEx Account No.: 933613038 &gt; Next &gt; Scroll to the bottom of License Agreement &gt; I accept &gt; Send </p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Status: Subscription Current</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Navigate to FedEx Freight Box tab &gt; FedEx Box Account #:  933613038 &gt; Verify Freight Box Account &gt; Verified</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Status: Subscription Current</p></li></ol><h2 class=\"ghq-card-content__medium-heading\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"MEDIUM_HEADING\">Additional PostalMate Settings to Check</h2><ol start=\"1\" class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST\"><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Insurance Settings &gt; Alternate Insurance setup &gt; Map services to coverage &gt; Map FedEx Freight Economy and FedEx Freight Priority</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Shipping Settings: Click Service Display tab &gt;&gt; Carrier-branded &gt; Enable Fedex Freight Box within FedEx and the All Carriers tab</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Freight Settings: Set Store Requirements and Enable Instructions Upon Completion if applicable</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Departments &amp; Products &gt; Map &gt; Shipping tab: Verify Shipping &amp; Insurance Charges are mapped &gt; Ok</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Label Settings &gt; FedEx Freight Box DV Warning, FedEx Freight Box BOL, &amp; FedEx Freight Box Addrs Lbl are assigned to 4x6 Thermal Label Printer</p></li></ol>",
        "owner": {
            "status": "ACTIVE",
            "email": "abraham@pcsynergy.com",
            "firstName": "Abraham",
            "lastName": "Udom"
        },
