        "content": "<p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">UPS Next Day Air Early has a hidden $30.00 Surcharge which does NOT get any incentive discounts.  Therefore, the $30.00 Surcharge needs to be subtracted from the Published Rate as well as the Wholesale Rate, in order to verify the actual % discount that should apply.  See the math below.......</p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Example: Level 1 Discount = 15% for UPS Next Day Air Early Letter &amp; Package</p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Step 1: Verify your UPS Discount Level in PM &gt; Tools &gt; PM Settings &gt; Carrier Setup &gt; UPS tab</p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Step 2: Go to the UPS Early Service in PM &gt; Tools &gt; PM Settings &gt; Set Shipping Rates</p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Step 3: Under View: Make note of the Published Rate and the Wholesale Rate</p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Step 4: Subtract the $30.00 Surcharge from each rate</p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Step 5: Multiply the % discount by the final Published Rate</p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Step 6: Subtract the amount of the discount from the Published Rate........This should equal the Wholesale Rate - $30.00.</p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\"><strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Published = $59.37,   Wholesale = $54.96,  Level 1 Discount = 15%</strong></p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\"><strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">$59.37 - $30.00 surcharge = $29.37;   $29.37 x 15% Disc. = $4.41;  $29.37 - $4.41 = $24.96</strong></p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\"><strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">$54.96 wholesale - $30.00 surcharge = $24.96</strong></p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\"><strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Thus, the Discount %, wholesale from published is correct. However, it will not match what shows in the tables due to the $30.00 surcharge being factored in.</strong></p>",
