        "content": "<p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Flex only supports Shipment for Walgreens store </p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">It has Customer ID check box in Customer screen.</p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">LTS = Long term support for Walgreen</p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\"> Walgreens is using Melissa data</p><ul start=\"1\" class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST\"><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">The receipt shipment prints on Thermal printer. as well as Label in Thermal printer</p></li></ul>",
