        "content": "<hr class=\"ghq-card-content__horizontal-rule\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"DIVIDER\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">A PostalMate network consists of:</p><ul start=\"1\" class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST\"><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">A Windows network. &nbsp;All computers (workstations) must be connected via a Windows network. &nbsp;Wireless networks are not supported. </p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">One Master station. &nbsp;This workstation contains a database shared by all workstations.</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">One or more Auxiliary station(s). &nbsp;These have PostalMate installed, but rely on the Master and its database.</p></li></ul><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">All workstations may share a report printer, but each station must have its own: label printer; receipt printer (if you use CashMate); and electronic scale (optional). &nbsp;Workstations that use the internet for shipping and other functionality may share a high-speed Internet connection across the network.</p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Make sure to look at the current <a href=\"http://www.pcsynergy.com/pdfs/hardware/hardwarereq.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"ghq-card-content__link\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"LINK\">Hardware Requirements</a> for updated information on hardware and networking.</p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">See TechNote titled <a href=\"http://www.pcsynergy.com/pdfs/networking/pmnetwork.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"ghq-card-content__link\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"LINK\">Networking PostalMate</a> for detailed instructions on setting up your PostalMate network.</p>",
