        "content": "<hr class=\"ghq-card-content__horizontal-rule\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"DIVIDER\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Microsoft is ending support for Windows 7, service pack 1, on January 14th, 2020.  </p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">This means that Microsoft will no longer provide security updates or support for any PCs running Windows 7.</p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">This also means that PostalMate will no longer support Windows 7 after this date.  Now is a good time to think about replacing any Windows 7 computers that you may have on your PostalMate network. </p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Our recommendation is to follow the current Hardware Requirements when making the decision to purchase a new computer.  We <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">do not</strong> recommend updating the operating system on a computer that does not meet current hardware requirements to Windows 10. </p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\"><a href=\"http://www.pcsynergy.com/pdfs/hardware/hardwarereq.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"ghq-card-content__link\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"LINK\">PostalMate Hardware Requirements</a></p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\"><a href=\"http://www.microsoft.com/en-us/windowsforbusiness/end-of-windows-7-support\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"ghq-card-content__link\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"LINK\">Microsoft end of life notice for Windows 7</a></p>",
