        "content": "<hr class=\"ghq-card-content__horizontal-rule\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"DIVIDER\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">From CashMate, you will go into the Mailbox Manager &gt; Tools &gt; Settings <span class=\"ghq-card-content__image-container\"><img class=\"ghq-card-content__image\" style=\"width:650px\" src=\"https://api.getguru.com/files/view/a07fba15-0c46-4969-bdd8-bc9304beece4\" width=\"650\" alt=\"Raise MB $ .2.png\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"IMAGE\" data-ghq-card-content-image-filename=\"Raise MB $ .2.png\"></span></p><hr class=\"ghq-card-content__horizontal-rule\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"DIVIDER\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">  <span class=\"ghq-card-content__image-container\"><img class=\"ghq-card-content__image\" style=\"width:650px\" src=\"https://api.getguru.com/files/view/9da74ed5-89cf-419f-a439-a164fb3d2b9a\" width=\"650\" alt=\"MB increase 2.png\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"IMAGE\" data-ghq-card-content-image-filename=\"MB increase 2.png\"></span></p><ul start=\"1\" class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST\"><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">From Settings &gt; Sizes and rates &gt; adjust your prices (remember, the term prices increase is based on what you enter as the monthly rate)</p></li></ul><hr class=\"ghq-card-content__horizontal-rule\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"DIVIDER\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\"><span class=\"ghq-card-content__image-container\"><img class=\"ghq-card-content__image\" style=\"width:650px\" src=\"https://api.getguru.com/files/view/ea4216d8-e623-4651-865a-5b933e3d6a4b\" width=\"650\" alt=\"legacy rates.png\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"IMAGE\" data-ghq-card-content-image-filename=\"legacy rates.png\"></span></p><ul start=\"1\" class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST\"><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">When it is time to do your renewals, it will default to your new prices, but you will have the option for legacy pricing for renewal.</p></li></ul>",
