        "content": "<hr class=\"ghq-card-content__horizontal-rule\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"DIVIDER\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">USPS ELS Error \"An error occurred in the secure channel support\" indicates an issue with using a secure browser. </p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">To resolve this problem, you will need to access Internet Explorer Options and turn off TLS 1.0 and 1.1 as well as SSL 3.0.  Internet Explorer version 11.0 or higher is necessary. </p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Endicia no longer supports Windows XP or Windows Vista due to these security restrictions. </p>",
