        "content": "<hr class=\"ghq-card-content__horizontal-rule\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"DIVIDER\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">This error indicates an issue with your FedEx account.  Please contact FedEx billing to verify account status.  </p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">There is a wide range of issues that can cause this error, including but not limited to: FedEx account number compromised, FedEx account payment issues including an expired credit card on file, trying to use a new FedEx account before the FedEx \"start\" date for the new account, etc.</p>",
