        "content": "<p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">If you are receiving error 8004: Invalid Meter number when attempting to process a FedEx Shipment, you will need to re-subscribe your FedEx account in PostalMate. Here is how: </p><ol start=\"1\" class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST\"><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Open PostalMate on your master station</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Choose <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Tools &gt; PostalMate Settings</strong></p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Select <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Carrier Setup</strong></p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Select the <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">FedEx </strong>tab</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">On the right side of the screen, below <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Online shipping</strong>, choose <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Subscribe online with FedEx</strong>. </p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Follow the online screens to verify your store and contact information, as well as your FedEx account number and complete the subscription. </p></li></ol><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Once subscribed, try your shipment again. </p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\"><span class=\"ghq-card-content__image-container\"><img class=\"ghq-card-content__image\" style=\"width:650px\" src=\"https://api.getguru.com/files/view/bb4f9311-a47d-4000-a46d-34e1ee480fe2\" width=\"650\" alt=\"image.png\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"IMAGE\" data-ghq-card-content-image-filename=\"image.png\"></span></p>",
