        "content": "<hr class=\"ghq-card-content__horizontal-rule\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"DIVIDER\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">This is more informational than an actual error.  When completing a carrier pickup for the day and receiving this message, FedEx is reporting that you shipped no packages on your account through PostalMate today. FedEx will not issue a closing report when no packages have been manifested. You may however, have drop-offs that you recorded in PostalMate.  No action is required on your part and you may continue as usual.</p>",
