    {
        "content": "<hr class=\"ghq-card-content__horizontal-rule\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"DIVIDER\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Possible solutions for random Access Violation errors in PostalMate.</p><h3 class=\"ghq-card-content__small-heading\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"SMALL_HEADING\">default printer reset</h3><ol start=\"1\" class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST\"><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">With PostalMate open, access Windows &gt; Control Panel &gt; Devices and Printers</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Right-click any printer and select Set as Default</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Close PostalMate</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">In Devices and Printers &gt; right click the correct printer and select set as default</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Relaunch PostalMate<span class=\"ghq-card-content__image-container\"><img class=\"ghq-card-content__image\" style=\"width:650px\" src=\"https://api.getguru.com/files/view/833ee8c6-e390-4e77-b9a3-c262a2ef3163\" width=\"650\" alt=\"image.png\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"IMAGE\" data-ghq-card-content-image-filename=\"image.png\"></span></p></li></ol><h3 class=\"ghq-card-content__small-heading\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"SMALL_HEADING\">Pro pack default settings</h3><ol start=\"1\" class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST\"><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Tools &gt; PostalMate settings &gt; Pro Pack Settings &gt; [TAB] Materials &gt; Set Defaults</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Verify that every option has a Default Product selected</p></li></ol><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\"><span class=\"ghq-card-content__image-container\"><img class=\"ghq-card-content__image\" style=\"width:650px\" src=\"https://api.getguru.com/files/view/3448fe68-e8c8-47b6-b284-84151d7ea985\" width=\"650\" alt=\"image.png\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"IMAGE\" data-ghq-card-content-image-filename=\"image.png\"></span></p>",
