        "content": "<hr class=\"ghq-card-content__horizontal-rule\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"DIVIDER\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">USPS ELS Error: 12507 means \"The Certified Intermediary’s pass phrase is incorrect.\"  You will need to update your Endicia passphrase in PostalMate. </p><ul start=\"1\" class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST\"><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">In PostalMate, choose <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Tools &gt; PostalMate Settings</strong></p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Select <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Carrier Setup</strong> on the left pane</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Choose the <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">USPS</strong> tab</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Select the Endicia Settings button</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Here, on the <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Accounts</strong> tab, you may update your <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Endicia Account Passphrase</strong> </p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">If you do not know your passphrase, you will need to contact Endicia. </p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">If you have a separate account for Printable Postage, you may need to update your passphrase using the <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Printable Postage settings</strong> button as well. </p></li></ul><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\"><span class=\"ghq-card-content__image-container\"><img class=\"ghq-card-content__image\" style=\"width:600px\" src=\"https://api.getguru.com/files/view/90f84054-e074-4d30-aab1-af9f1a9ad163\" width=\"600\" alt=\"image.png\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"IMAGE\" data-ghq-card-content-image-filename=\"image.png\"></span></p>",
