        "content": "<hr class=\"ghq-card-content__horizontal-rule\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"DIVIDER\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">USPS ELS Error: 2021 indicates an incorrect tier level is set for USPS</p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\"><strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Error:</strong> Account &lt;account number&gt; is not qualified for RetailGround. Error encountered.</p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">USPS Retail Ground is only available for stores that do not use a discounted USPS tier and are set to Published Approved Shipper tier levels in PostalMate. Most stores use Commercial, RS Endicia, or Preferred discounted rate groups. This means that Retail Ground is not an option. However,  <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">USPS Parcel Select Ground</strong> is the comparable option, and is available to these discounted rate groups. </p><h2 class=\"ghq-card-content__medium-heading\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"MEDIUM_HEADING\">How to resolve</h2><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">If this error message is encountered, the customer needs to change their tier level to one of the three listed above (Commercial Base, RS Associates Postal Rates, or Endicia Preferred Rates). If you are unsure, select Commercial Base.  </p><ul start=\"1\" class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST\"><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">In PostalMate, choose to <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Tools &gt; PostalMate Settings</strong>. </p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Select <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Carrier Setup</strong> on the left pane</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Select the <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">USPS</strong> tab</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Select the button below <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Wholesale Rates.  </strong>Select the <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Pricing Group</strong> that your store belongs to.  If you are not sure, select Commercial Base</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Click <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Apply</strong> and close <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">PostalMate Settings</strong></p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\"><strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">USPS Parcel Select Ground</strong> will now be an available option.  However, you may need to enable the service on your Service display tabs.  See below.</p></li></ul><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\"><span class=\"ghq-card-content__image-container\"><img class=\"ghq-card-content__image\" style=\"width:600px\" src=\"https://api.getguru.com/files/view/c1d24b4a-ecf4-4a24-b060-3c56f937b9e9\" width=\"600\" alt=\"image.png\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"IMAGE\" data-ghq-card-content-image-filename=\"image.png\"></span></p><h2 class=\"ghq-card-content__medium-heading\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"MEDIUM_HEADING\">Service Display</h2><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">You may also need to enable USPS Parcel Select Ground in <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Service Display</strong>. </p><ul start=\"1\" class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST\"><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Remain in <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">PostalMate Settings</strong></p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Select <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Shipping Settings</strong> on the left pane</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Select the <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Service Display</strong> tab </p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Select a tab you wish for <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">USPS Parcel Select Ground</strong> to display, such as Post Office, or USPS. </p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Click the \"<strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">&gt;</strong>\" in front of <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">United States Postal Service</strong> to expand and see the services</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Look for <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">USPS Parcel Select Ground</strong> and check mark the box in front of it. </p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Repeat the above steps for any other tab you wish for this service to display. </p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Choose <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Save </strong>and close <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">PostalMate Settings</strong>. </p></li></ul><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\"><span class=\"ghq-card-content__image-container\"><img class=\"ghq-card-content__image\" style=\"width:600px\" src=\"https://api.getguru.com/files/view/e321dcc4-0255-42b2-aa17-ec4cddf6b90b\" width=\"600\" alt=\"image.png\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"IMAGE\" data-ghq-card-content-image-filename=\"image.png\"></span></p>",
