        "content": "<hr class=\"ghq-card-content__horizontal-rule\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"DIVIDER\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">This is for debit and charge accounts. Click on <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Yes</strong> to proceed with the transaction, and override the limit..</p><h2 class=\"ghq-card-content__medium-heading\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"MEDIUM_HEADING\">How to get to Account Balance Limit</h2><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">You will see the \"Account Balance Limit\" prompt if the customer’s account limit will be exceeded by the current transaction.</p>",
