        "content": "<hr class=\"ghq-card-content__horizontal-rule\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"DIVIDER\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">When a customer has more than one account assigned to them, you will need to select which account will be used for the current transaction.</p><ol start=\"1\" class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST\"><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Select the desired account.</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Click <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">OK</strong>.</p></li></ol><h2 class=\"ghq-card-content__medium-heading\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"MEDIUM_HEADING\">How to get to the Select Account dialog</h2><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">In the CashMate Register window, from the main menu choose <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Edit </strong>&gt; <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Customer</strong>, and go to the \"<strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Accounts</strong>\" tab.</p>",
