        "content": "<hr class=\"ghq-card-content__horizontal-rule\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"DIVIDER\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">This is where you can open a new Credit, Invoice or Debit account for the currently selected customer. Typically a customer would have only one account linked to it, however any combination of up to 50 credit and/or debit accounts can be linked to a single customer.</p><h2 class=\"ghq-card-content__medium-heading\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"MEDIUM_HEADING\">Account Name</h2><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Type in the name of the Account here. This can be either a special account for the customer only, or an accounting firm's name which handle's the customer's billing.</p><h2 class=\"ghq-card-content__medium-heading\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"MEDIUM_HEADING\">Account Type</h2><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Select the type of account:</p><ul start=\"1\" class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST\"><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\"><a href=\"http://www.pcsynergy.com/pdfs/pos/invoice.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"ghq-card-content__link\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"LINK\">Credit</a></p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\"><a href=\"http://www.pcsynergy.com/pdfs/pos/invoice.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"ghq-card-content__link\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"LINK\">Invoice</a></p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\"><a href=\"http://www.pcsynergy.com/pdfs/pos/debitacct.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"ghq-card-content__link\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"LINK\">Debit</a></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"ghq-card-content__medium-heading\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"MEDIUM_HEADING\">Statement Group</h2><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Select the Statement Group that this customer will be assigned to. <a href=\"Add_Edit_Statement_Groups.htm#Establishing_Statement_Groups\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"ghq-card-content__link\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"LINK\">Statement Groups</a> usually denote the billing cycle type: First of Month, Middle of Month.</p><h2 class=\"ghq-card-content__medium-heading\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"MEDIUM_HEADING\">Balance Forward</h2><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">If this is an existing charge account customer (from another system) with an existing balance to forward, type in the balance amount here.</p><h2 class=\"ghq-card-content__medium-heading\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"MEDIUM_HEADING\">About credit, invoice and debit Accounts</h2><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Customer credit or debit account features are fully integrated into the CashMate Register. Ringing up an account sale is just as easy as a cash sale. Here are some of the things you can do when you set up a customer account:</p><ul start=\"1\" class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST\"><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Set up either a credit, invoice or debit account</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Print account statements</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Print AR, Delinquency, invoice aging and other account reports</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Keep track of account histories</p></li></ul><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Customer account information is stored and managed in the Customer Database.</p><h2 class=\"ghq-card-content__medium-heading\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"MEDIUM_HEADING\">How to get to the \"Open New Account\" dialog —</h2><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">From the <a href=\"Find_Customer.htm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"ghq-card-content__link\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"LINK\">Customer</a> window, select the <a href=\"Add_Edit_Customer.htm#Accounts_Customer\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"ghq-card-content__link\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"LINK\">Accounts</a> tab. Click on the \"Open New\" button.</p>",
