        "content": "<hr class=\"ghq-card-content__horizontal-rule\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"DIVIDER\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">This is where you can open a credit, debit, or invoice account for the selected customer. This is also where to view and change the details in an existing account, when using the Edit &gt; Customer option.</p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Note: this tab is visible in CashMate register, not in PostalMate.</p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">The following TechNotes are available and include detailed information on setting up the following types of accounts.</p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\"><a href=\"http://www.pcsynergy.com/pdfs/pos/creditacct.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"ghq-card-content__link\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"LINK\">Credit Accounts</a></p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\"><a href=\"http://www.pcsynergy.com/pdfs/pos/debitacct.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"ghq-card-content__link\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"LINK\">Debit Accounts</a></p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\"><a href=\"http://www.pcsynergy.com/pdfs/pos/invoice.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"ghq-card-content__link\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"LINK\">Invoice Accounts</a></p><h2 class=\"ghq-card-content__medium-heading\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"MEDIUM_HEADING\">How to get to the Customer Accounts tab</h2><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">In the CashMate Register, choose Edit &gt; Customer, select a customer and choose Edit. Select the Accounts tab.</p>",
