        "content": "<hr class=\"ghq-card-content__horizontal-rule\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"DIVIDER\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">This report lists all customers that have charge accounts in your store, including account summary information. You can choose to sort it by Customer ID or by Statement Group.</p><h2 class=\"ghq-card-content__medium-heading\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"MEDIUM_HEADING\">How to print the Charge Account Report</h2><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">From the Charge Account Report dialog:</p><ol start=\"1\" class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST\"><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Select the desired sorting option.</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Click on the <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Print</strong> button.</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Follow the printing instructions in the print dialog.</p></li></ol><h2 class=\"ghq-card-content__medium-heading\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"MEDIUM_HEADING\">How to get to the Charge Account Report dialog:</h2><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">From the CashMate register screen, select <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Reports&nbsp;&gt; Accounts Receivable&nbsp;&gt; Charge Account</strong>.</p>",
