        "content": "<hr class=\"ghq-card-content__horizontal-rule\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"DIVIDER\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">This report lists all customers that have debit accounts in your store, and includes summary account information.</p><h2 class=\"ghq-card-content__medium-heading\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"MEDIUM_HEADING\">How to get to Debit Account Report</h2><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Choose <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Reports &gt; Accounts Receivable &gt; Debit Accounts.</strong></p>",
