        "content": "<hr class=\"ghq-card-content__horizontal-rule\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"DIVIDER\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">This is where you can set Accounts Receivable <a href=\"Default_settings.htm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"ghq-card-content__link\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"LINK\">defaults</a>, to help make setting up new customer accounts easier.</p><ul start=\"1\" class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST\"><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Here you may also customize the customer billing statement information.</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Move the cursor to any field that you want to change.</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Each field’s description and usage is provided below.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"ghq-card-content__medium-heading\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"MEDIUM_HEADING\">Defaults</h2><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">These settings control the auto-fill information in the <a href=\"Open_New_Account.htm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"ghq-card-content__link\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"LINK\">Open New&nbsp;Account</a> and <a href=\"Add_Edit_Statement_Groups.htm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"ghq-card-content__link\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"LINK\">Statement Group</a> dialogs.</p><ul start=\"1\" class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST\"><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Credit Limit: Enter the amount here that you want as the default charge limit in new accounts. The limit can be overridden individually in each customer record.</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Debit Deposit: Enter the default deposit amount that you want to collect for new debit accounts. This amount can be overridden individually in each customer record.</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Debit Deposit Low: Enter the minimum dollar amount that you want to allow new debit accounts. This amount can be overridden on an individual basis.</p></li></ul><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Note: During a transaction, when the customer's account deposit level reaches the \"Debit Deposit Low\" amount, the \"LOW DEPOSIT BALANCE WARNING!\" message will display. The projected account<br>balance <em class=\"ghq-card-content__italic\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"ITALIC\">after the transaction</em> will also be noted.</p><ul start=\"1\" class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST\"><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\"><strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Due Day</strong>: Whatever you choose here will be the default Due Day when you set up a new <a href=\"Add_Edit_Statement_Groups.htm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"ghq-card-content__link\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"LINK\">Statement<br>Group</a>. It can be overridden in the Statement Group dialog. You have six choices: The 1st, 5th, 10th, 15th, 20th or Last Day of the month.</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\"><strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Late Fee Amount</strong>: If you assess a flat amount late fee for past due accounts, regardless of the balance due, type that amount into this field. This setting will override any entry you make in the Late Fee<br>Percent setting.</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\"><strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Late Fee Percent</strong>: &nbsp;If you assess late fees for past due accounts, and your charges are based on a percentage of the balance due, enter that percentage here.</p></li></ul><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Note: If an amount is entered in the <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Late Fee Amount</strong> field, it will override any percentage entered here.</p><ul start=\"1\" class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST\"><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\"><strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Late Fee Days</strong>: Type in the number of days to let pass before late charges are applied to an overdue<br>account.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"ghq-card-content__medium-heading\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"MEDIUM_HEADING\">How to get to the \"Accounts Receivable Settings\" dialog —</h2><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">From the CashMate register screen, select <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Tools&nbsp;</strong>&gt; <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Options&nbsp;</strong>&gt; <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Accounts Receivable Settings</strong>, choose the<br><strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Defaults</strong> tab.</p>",
