    {
        "content": "<hr class=\"ghq-card-content__horizontal-rule\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"DIVIDER\"><h2 class=\"ghq-card-content__medium-heading\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"MEDIUM_HEADING\">Statements</h2><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">These options allow you to customize messages and specify other information to appear on each customer’s account statement as well as set up for email delivery of statements.&nbsp;</p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">See TechNote titled <a href=\"http://www.pcsynergy.com/pdfs/pos/CreatePrintEmailAR.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"ghq-card-content__link\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"LINK\">Create, Print and Email AR Statements</a> for detailed information on setting up and using Credit Account statements.&nbsp;</p><h2 class=\"ghq-card-content__medium-heading\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"MEDIUM_HEADING\">Settings for All statements (Credit and Invoice)</h2><ul start=\"1\" class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST\"><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\"><strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Include store information</strong>: Check this box to include your Store Information on customer statements.</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\"><strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Include late warning</strong>: Check this box to automatically apply a late warning on statements for customers whose bills are past due.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"ghq-card-content__medium-heading\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"MEDIUM_HEADING\">Settings for Credit account statements</h2><ul start=\"1\" class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST\"><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Print/Email for zero balances: Check this box if you want to print statements for customers that have no outstanding balances.</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Print/Email for negative balances: Where your store owes money to customer(s), check this box if you want to print statements for those customers.</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Include Ship To address: Statements will include ship to address for shipments.</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Include tracking number: Statements will include tracking number for shipments.</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Include Ship To detail: Check this box if you wish the Ship To detail from shipments to appear on the statements.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"ghq-card-content__medium-heading\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"MEDIUM_HEADING\">Settings for Invoice account Statements</h2><ul start=\"1\" class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST\"><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Print/Email for accounts with activity: When checked, mass statements will print for accounts with a balance due, and when there is activity (including no balance due).</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Include Ship To address: Statements will include ship to address for shipments.</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Include tracking number: Statements will include tracking number for shipments.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"ghq-card-content__medium-heading\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"MEDIUM_HEADING\">Email delivery</h2><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">You can designate in-house credit account to have their monthly statements sent via email, as HTML attachments.</p><ul start=\"1\" class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST\"><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Check the <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Enabled</strong> box to turn on email statements.</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Enter in Store name, email subject line, URL for a custom logo and the text in the body of the email. Check the box to <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Copy emails to store</strong> if desired.</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Choose the <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Setup for accounts</strong> button to designate accounts for print, email or print &amp; email.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"ghq-card-content__medium-heading\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"MEDIUM_HEADING\">How to get to Statements settings</h2><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Choose <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Tools </strong>&gt; <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Options </strong>&gt; <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Accounts Receivable Settings</strong>. Choose the Statements tab</p>",
