        "content": "<hr class=\"ghq-card-content__horizontal-rule\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"DIVIDER\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">The <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Account Statement Delivery Method</strong> screen allows you to set the delivery method for statements to Print, Email, or both Print &amp; Email for all existing accounts.</p><ol start=\"1\" class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST\"><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Select one or more accounts, then select <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Print</strong>, <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Email</strong> or <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Print &amp; Emai</strong>l from the drop down list. Use the <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Select All </strong>button to choose all accounts.</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Each account must include an email address in order to set it up for email delivery.</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__numbered-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"NUMBERED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Click <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">OK</strong> to save your changes.</p></li></ol><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">The delivery method can also be changed by editing the customer account in the CashMate register. From <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Edit </strong>&gt; <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Customer</strong>, find the customer you wish to view and select <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Edit</strong>. Choose the <a href=\"Customer_Accounts.htm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"ghq-card-content__link\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"LINK\">Accounts</a> tab.</p><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">See TechNote titled <a href=\"http://www.pcsynergy.com/pdfs/pos/CreatePrintEmailAR.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"ghq-card-content__link\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"LINK\">Create, Print &amp; Email AR Statements</a> for detailed information on setup and using AR Statements.</p><h2 class=\"ghq-card-content__medium-heading\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"MEDIUM_HEADING\">How to get to Account Statement Delivery Method</h2><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Choose <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Tools </strong>&gt; <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Options </strong>&gt; <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Accounts Receivable Settings</strong>. Choose the <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Statements </strong>tab and select the <strong class=\"ghq-card-content__bold\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BOLD\">Setup for Accounts button</strong>.</p>",
