        "content": "<hr class=\"ghq-card-content__horizontal-rule\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"DIVIDER\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">\"PC Synergy Premium Services\" are enhanced features in PostalMate that utilize PC Synergy data center servers. Examples of Premium Services are <a href=\"FedEx_Internet_Shipping_Overview.htm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"ghq-card-content__link\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"LINK\">FedEx internet shipping</a>, <a href=\"DHL_internet_shipping_overview.htm\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"ghq-card-content__link\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"LINK\">DHL internet shipping</a>, and features using UPS Online Tools®.</p><h2 class=\"ghq-card-content__medium-heading\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"MEDIUM_HEADING\">Getting authorization for PC Synergy Premium Services</h2><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">The following requirements must be met before your PostalMate system will<br>have access PC Synergy Premium Services:</p><ul start=\"1\" class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST\"><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\"><a href=\"http://pcsynergy.com/pdfs/shipping/premiumservices.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"ghq-card-content__link\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"LINK\">Premium Services Agreement.</a> You must sign the PC Synergy Premium Services Agreement. You may download this agreement from the support pages of <a href=\"http://www.pcsynergy.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"ghq-card-content__link\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"LINK\">www.pcsynergy.com</a>. Read it carefully, sign it and return it to PC Synergy via fax at (760) 536-8233.</p></li><li class=\"ghq-card-content__bulleted-list-item\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"BULLETED_LIST_ITEM\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">Support status. You must be a currently supported PC Synergy customer in good standing.</p></li></ul>",
