        "content": "<hr class=\"ghq-card-content__horizontal-rule\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"DIVIDER\"><p class=\"ghq-card-content__paragraph\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"paragraph\">As of January 27th, 2019, the discount for First Class Mail letter is .05 when using Printable Postage.  We have sent out a couple of eUpdates to change from .03 to .05.  However, you may use the following script in case the issue comes up again in the future. </p><pre class=\"ghq-card-content__code-block\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"CODE_BLOCK\" data-ghq-code-block-syntax=\"Plain Text\" data-ghq-code-block-prism=\"plain\"><code class=\"ghq-card-content__code-block-line\" data-ghq-card-content-type=\"CODE_BLOCK_LINE\">UPDATE CARRIERONLINESETTINGS SET COSVALUE = 0.05 WHERE CARRIERONLINESETTINGSID = 30^ SET TERM ; </code></pre>",
